rows.label: tev045302_MSG0001
rows.name: I feel shame for worrying Hala.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045302_MSG0002
rows.name: But I cannot find strength to dance like I used to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045302_MSG0003
rows.name: I miss Quegga. I want to be held in his arms again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045302_MSG0005
rows.name:
Did Hala send for you?
If you want to talk to her, she is over there.[ST:wait ]
